 /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6f724bda2e01ae9ee95769a15b27dc82af960e","tid":1609983,"uid":70493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:11:13.000Z","msg":"由教育局宣佈停課，同罷課相差好遠喎..."},{"pid":"8321c7fff9d1e1028220071b295c0a567af1fd4f","tid":1609983,"uid":257736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:41:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://t.me/klt1300\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fklt1300&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVmzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=8030b7f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/klt1300</a><br />\n九龍塘 罷工 集會<br />\n又一城見"}]}